1593
02:00:12,220 --> 02:00:16,819
So certain of your
world. Of what's real.

1594
02:00:16,820 --> 02:00:18,820
Do you think he is?

1595
02:00:20,420 --> 02:00:23,520
Or do you think he's
as lost as I was?

1596
02:00:24,520 --> 02:00:26,220
