1597
02:00:28,120 --> 02:00:30,620
No creeping doubts?

1598
02:00:31,120 --> 02:00:33,920
Not feeling persecuted, Dom?

1599
02:00:34,020 --> 02:00:35,519
Chased around the globe...

1600
02:00:35,520 --> 02:00:38,319
