question your reality
came from me.

1634
02:02:57,020 --> 02:03:00,320
You planted the idea in my mind?

1635
02:03:01,620 --> 02:03:03,320
What is she talking about?

1636
02:03:04,020 --> 02:03:07,027
The reason I knew
inception was possible

1637
02:03:07,028 --> 02:03:09,520
