1680
02:07:46,820 --> 02:07:48,863
That means he's down
here somewhere.

1681
02:07:48,864 --> 02:07:50,520
That means I have to find him.

1682
02:07:52,320 --> 02:07:55,619
I can't stay with her any more,
because she doesn't exist.

1683
02:07:55,620 --> 02:07:59,219
